These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-3-1::.
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: november, october
2 different games are played: canasta, mah-jongg
1. the person who's birthday is in october is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in november##3
2. the person playing mah-jongg is on the right of the person who's birthday is in october##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |  1   |   2   |
| Birthday   | october  | november |
| Game       | canasta | mah-jongg |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-3-2::.
House: ranch-style, art-deco
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: daffodil, zinnia
1. the person who growszinnia is on the left or right of the art-deco house##3
2. the art-deco house is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |   2   |
| House   | ranch-style | art-deco |
| Flower      | zinnia     | daffodil  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-3-3::.
The people use 2 different means of transport: boat, motorbike
2 different pets are kept: dog, ferret
1. the owner of the dog is on the left of the person driving the motorbike##1
2. the owner of the dog is on the left or right of the person driving the motorbike##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |
| Transport   | boat | motorbike  |
| Pet   | dog | ferret |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-3-4::.
2 different pets are kept: mouse, rabbit
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: january, february
1. the person who's birthday is in january is on the right of the owner of the rabbit##1
2. the owner of the mouse is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |    2    |
| Pet   | rabbit | mouse   |
| Birthday       | february | january |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-3-5::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: hiking, card-games
There 2 different types of food: avocado, apple
1. the person eating apple is on the right of the person who's hobby is card-games##1
2. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is hiking##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |
| Hobby   | card-games    | hiking    |
| Food   | avocado | apple |

